FILE
	/usr/common/sys/configd.c

NAME
	set_shutdown_message - set the text of the shutdown message

PROTOTYPE
	void set_shutdown_message(string new_message)

CALLED BY
	System, Common, Game

DESCRIPTION
	Set the system shutdown message.  This message will be sent to
	incoming connections when the MUD is in the process of shutting
	down.

RETURN VALUE
	None.

ERRORS
	Normally none.

SEE ALSO
	set_welcome_message, get_shutdown_message, set_suspended_message
